CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 12, 1941, pg. 8, reads: "Pretty Jackson-Cralle Nuptials Bring Socialites Together In Festive Affair - The Jackson-Cralle nuptials last Saturday evening proved one of smoke town's smartest affairs...Mrs. John Jackson, mother of the bride, Mrs. Joseph Cralle, mother of the groom... - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Mrs. John Jackson and Mrs. Joseph Cralle standing behind table with flowers, possibly in Loendi Club, for Jackson - Cralle wedding
